<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#112512><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/ufizbanic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fizbanic</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 100<br> <font color=#CCCCC8>(4/18/01 9:44:59 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/fizbanic/fizbanic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Shadows of Luclin... EQ2? Release 12/03/01</span><hr size=1> Well I don't think you could really call this EQ2 as they've stated that it is a add-on as well only one new race.<br>
<br>
When I finally read the announcement all I could thing of was DragonLance.<br>
<br>
I can't recall what book it was in but,  Kitiara and Sturm ended up going to the moon on a gnomish flying craft and for some reason this seems simular in a fashion.<br>
<br>
Mind you as with any of you other addicts out there I will more than likely be placing my order for it as well.  After work if it was possible.<br>
<br>
Although I don't think I like the acronym SoL,  Maybe they should have named it &quot;The addiction continues!&quot;<br>
<br>
Well maybe not as I think some of us are SoL when it comes to a RL. <p>Liddlerunt Wyldefeather 37th season Druid





