<br>
It was the closest place to hunt at level 5, especialy with the boats being as screwy as they were.  Not to mention there was a limited amount of people who were level 12 or higher to bind you someplace.<br>
<br>
I'm sounding like an oldtimer?<br>
(... and back when I was your age, we had to WALK to school in a huge blizzard!- Haha!)<br>
<br>
Now, with the addition of The Warrens and the Kobolds, I guess you could say, it's raining cats and dogs, over in Odus!<br>
<br>
Nyuk, nyuk, nyuk!<br>
